<includeonly>{{#invoke:ItemLink|main|id={{{1|{{{id|}}}}}}|count={{{2|{{{count|}}}}}}|noicon={{{noicon|}}}}}</includeonly><noinclude>
{{doc}}
Renders an inline item link with optional icon and count.

'''Usage:'''
* <code><nowiki>{{ItemLink|IronIngot}}</nowiki></code> — link with icon
* <code><nowiki>{{ItemLink|IronIngot|5}}</nowiki></code> — link with icon and ×5 count
* <code><nowiki>{{ItemLink|IronIngot|noicon=1}}</nowiki></code> — text link only

'''Parameters:'''
* '''1''' (or '''id'''): Item template identifier (required)
* '''2''' (or '''count'''): Quantity to display (optional)
* '''noicon''': Set to 1 to suppress the icon (optional)

[[Category:Link templates]]
</noinclude>
